Package: airsetup
Title: Setup AI-Assisted R Analysis Project Structures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("gestimation", "Toolkit", , "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight workflow infrastructure for setting up minimal
    AI-assisted R analysis projects. The package creates a controlled
    AI-visible project folder with source, dummy-data, AI-output, R-output,
    QC, and log areas, plus AGENTS.md guidance and a QC_STATUS.md tracker.
    In split mode, it also creates a sibling R execution folder for hidden
    analysis data that AI agents must not inspect. The package does not
    implement statistical analysis functions.
